window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A dying king. A mysterious invader. The seer's vision was clear: Find the lost shard from the Spire of Peace or the realm would drown in blood.&nbsp;</p> <p>The problem: Eight hundred years ago the elven hero Kathkalan took the shard with him into the lair of the most vicious dragon ever known to mankind...and he never returned.&nbsp;</p> <p>Reluctantly drafted to lead the quest is the minor noble Midas, torn between his duty to the realm and the desire to protect his sons. With an unlikely band of heroes, including two elderly rangers and a young tinkerâ€™s son, Midas must risk losing everything he loves if he is to locate the shard and save the Known Lands.</p>"; 
